# 0.5.0

-  Menu item to clear recent files
-  Only allow to save gpx files to avoid override with different format
-  Save data to disk
-  Show time in point popup
-  Use Ctrl+ primary button from map selection
-  Add elevation in distance calculation
-  Add total distance graph
-  connect switchs to show waypoints and graph points
-  Remove points
-  Add shortcuts for zoom in/out
-  Fix selection outside graph
-  Move selected point using keyboard
-  Allow select parts of track without start selection
-  Any surround of point allow to select it (half distance from prev/next points)
-  Detect active route in negative offsets

# 0.4.0

- Add metadata info
- Add 128 icon
- Add flatpak manifest
